How to run from maestria:

pip3 install --user jupyter 
pip3 install astropy --user --upgrade
pip3 install matplotlib --user --upgrade
pip3 install --user scipy
pip3 install --user progressbar2

Copy all the files from github (above) into a directory your want to work from.

The run:

~/.local/bin/ipython

In [1]: %pylab
In [2]: %run guPsc.py 1 1

The last command will run the program for GU Psc b for the 3rd night.
To get usage information:

In [3]: %run guPsc.py
Usage: FileNumber, StarNumber
 
 Filenumber 1-3: 
  1: Gu_variab_20141011_J_normlightcurve_GU_comp.txt
  2: Gu_variab_20141010_J_normlightcurve_GU_comp.txt
  3: Gu_variab_20131222_J_normlightcurve_GU_comp.txt
 
 Star Number: 
  1: GU Psc b
  2-8: comparision stars
 
 
To close all the pop-up windows type:

In [4]: close("all")
